nslation-origin=\"off\">Directive automatically applied to Angular form controls that sets CSS classes\nbased on control status.</p>\n\n\n  </section>\n<h2 id=\"exported-from\">Exported from<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatus#exported-from\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">ReactiveFormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/FormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">FormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  \n<section class=\"selector-list\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">选择器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatus#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/FormControlName\" class=\"code-anchor\">formControlName</a>]</code></li>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>]</code></li>\n    <li><code>[formControl]</code></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n  <section class=\"description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatus#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n    <h3 id=\"css-classes-applied\" translation-result=\"on\">应用的 CSS 类<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatus#css-classes-applied\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3><h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"css-classes-applied\">CSS classes applied<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatus#css-classes-applied\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">当这些属性变为 true 时，将应用以下类：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following classes are applied as the properties become true:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>ng-valid</li>\n<li>ng-invalid</li>\n<li>ng-pending</li>\n<li>ng-pristine</li>\n<li>ng-dirty</li>\n<li>ng-untouched</li>\n<li>ng-touched</li>\n</ul>\n\n  </section>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/NgControlStatusGroup\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/NgControlStatus#css-classes-applied\n - api/forms/NgControlStatus#description\n - api/forms/NgControlStatus#exported-from\n - api/forms/NgControlStatus#ngcontrolstatus\n - api/forms/NgControlStatus#selectors\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/forms/src/directives/ng_control_status.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L61-L96\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/13.2.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/directives/ng_control_status.ts#L61-L96\n-->"}